Full Stack Social Media App
рџљЂ Overview

A full-stack social media web application built using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and EJS.
It allows users to register, authenticate securely, create posts, like/unlike content, and manage their profiles including profile picture uploads.

рџ› пёЏ Tech Stack
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB (Mongoose)
Frontend: EJS, HTML, CSS
Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
Security: bcrypt for password hashing
File Upload: Multer
Other: Cookie-parser, dotenv

