вљ™пёЏ Installation & Setup
Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Prathvik8/miniproject
cd social-media-app
Install dependencies
npm install
Create a .env file
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
Run the server
node app.js
Open in browser
http://localhost:3000
                      
